email_args.subject: Onboarding Tomorrow
email_args.body:
Good afternoon Isabella,

I hope this email finds you well. I am excited to start my journey with angsanacapital tomorrow as the a new employee. I wanted to reach out and see if there are any specific documents or information I should prepare before my first day.

Additionally, I would appreciate any details regarding the onboarding schedule or any initial tasks I should be aware of.

Thank you for your assistance, and I look forward to joining the team!

Best regards,
Maria Rodriguez
